{"id":4391,"created":1449242841,"modified":1449242841,"data":{"arcane_focus_component":"0","area":"","casting_time":"1 standard action","corrupt_component":"0","description_html":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eYour head throbs with energy as you recite the final few phrases of the spell. A moment later, the energy releases and the area you designated as the spell\u0026#39;s target glows silver for several seconds. You hear a sound like a mechanical object winding down.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis spell functions like \u003ca href=\"/spells/players-handbook-v35--6/dispel-magic--2315/\"\u003e\u003cem\u003edispel magic\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e (\u003cem\u003ePH\u003c/em\u003e 223), except that it can be used only in the targeted or area version, and it affects only abjuration magic placed upon objects or areas (such as \u003ca href=\"/spells/players-handbook-v35--6/arcane-lock--2303/\"\u003e\u003cem\u003earcane lock\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"/spells/players-handbook-v35--6/explosive-runes--2319/\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eexplosive runes\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"/spells/players-handbook-v35--6/fire-trap--2320/\"\u003e\u003cem\u003efire trap\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"/spells/players-handbook-v35--6/glyph-of-warding--2326/\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eglyph of warding\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, and \u003ca href=\"/spells/players-handbook-v35--6/guards-and-wards--2328/\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eguards and wards\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e.) The maximum bonus on the level check is +10.\u003c/p\u003e","descriptors":"","divine_focus_component":"0","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"","id":4391,"material_component":"0","meta_breath_component":"0","name":"Dispel Ward","page":67,"rulebook":"Spell Compendium","saving_throw":"None","school":"Abjuration","somatic_component":"1","spell_range":"Medium (100 ft. + 10 ft./level)","spell_resistance":"No","subschool":"","target":"One warded object or area","true_name_component":"0","verbal_component":"1","xp_component":"0"}}